      <title>凯雷加入私募基金热潮，瞄准欧洲富人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-13/carlyle-joins-rush-of-private-credit-funds-tapping-europe-s-rich-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[凯雷集团 (Carlyle Group Inc.) 正与黑石集团 (Blackstone Inc.) 等巨头一道，竞相争夺欧洲大陆富裕投资者持有的数万亿美元资金，并正在为富裕个人准备其首个欧洲私人信贷基金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-13/carlyle-joins-rush-of-private-credit-funds-tapping-europe-s-rich-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
