      <title>随着市场收紧，石油输出国组织 (OPEC) 前景展望之前油价走高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-13</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有迹象表明现货原油市场正在收紧，油价小幅走高，随着欧佩克继续实施供应限制以支撑价格，交易员也在等待欧佩克的市场前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-13</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Feb 2024 23:44:51 GMT</pubDate>
